The risk is here.

23:30.560 --> 23:37.480
Entry to stop and the distribution to your target down here.

23:37.480 --> 23:46.200
Risk to reward ratio better than 8 to 1 and using a hypothetical $100,000 demo account

23:46.200 --> 23:49.480
if you're doing one of those funded account challenges or whatever.

